title: Krishna Shroff on a marathon? Shares another topless picture
text: Krishna Shroff on a marathon? Shares another topless picture Friday, 16 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) Jackie Shroff's adorable daughter Krishna Shroff turned heads few months back with some of her topless images, guess it's time for another one to be floating on social media.
